00124 bool CompositeOFMultiply::evaluate_with_gradient( EvalType type, 
00125                                              PatchData& pd,
00126                                              double& value_out,
00127                                              std::vector<Vector3D>& grad_out,
00128                                              MsqError& err )
00129 {
00130   double value_2;
00131   bool ok;
00132   
00133   ok = objFunc1->evaluate_with_gradient( type, pd, value_out, grad_out, err );
00134   if (MSQ_CHKERR(err) || !ok) return false;
00135   ok = objFunc2->evaluate_with_gradient( type, pd, value_2, mGradient, err );
00136   if (MSQ_CHKERR(err) || !ok) return false;
00137   
00138   assert( grad_out.size() == pd.num_free_vertices() );
00139   assert( mGradient.size() == pd.num_free_vertices() );
00140   
00141   std::vector<Vector3D>::iterator i = grad_out.begin(), j = mGradient.begin();
00142   while (i != grad_out.end()) {
00143     *i *= value_2;
00144     *j *= value_out;
00145     *i += *j;
00146     ++i;
00147     ++j;
00148   }
00149   value_out *= value_2;
00150   return true;
00151 }

00153 bool CompositeOFMultiply::evaluate_with_Hessian_diagonal( EvalType type, 
00154                                             PatchData& pd,
00155                                             double& value_out,
00156                                             std::vector<Vector3D>& grad_out,
00157                                             std::vector<SymMatrix3D>& diag_out,
00158                                             MsqError& err )
00159 {
00160   double value_2;
00161   bool valid;
00162 
00163   valid = objFunc1->evaluate_with_Hessian_diagonal( type, pd, value_out, grad_out, diag_out, err );
00164   if (MSQ_CHKERR(err) || !valid) return false;
00165   valid = objFunc2->evaluate_with_Hessian_diagonal( type, pd, value_2, mGradient, mDiagonal, err );
00166   if (MSQ_CHKERR(err) || !valid) return false;
00167 
00168   for (size_t i = 0; i < pd.num_free_vertices(); ++i) {
00169     diag_out[i] *= value_2;
00170     mDiagonal[i] *= value_out;
00171     diag_out[i] += mDiagonal[i];
00172     diag_out[i] += outer_plus_transpose( grad_out[i], mGradient[i] );
00173 
00174     grad_out[i] *= value_2;
00175     mGradient[i] *= value_out;
00176     grad_out[i] += mGradient[i];
00177   }
00178   
00179   value_out *= value_2;
00180   return true;
